{"title":"Design-Audit-Polish 迭代闭环","uid":"07706b25f58b1ff646f771690c909541","slug":"Design-Audit-Polish 迭代闭环","date":"2026-06-27T07:33:53.000Z","updated":"2026-06-27T07:33:53.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Design-Audit-Polish 迭代闭环.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/claude.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Impeccable-插件的-Design-Audit-Polish-标准化设计迭代工作流\"><a href=\"#Impeccable-插件的-Design-Audit-Polish-标准化设计迭代工作流\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Impeccable 插件的 Design-Audit-Polish 标准化设计迭代工作流\"></a>Impeccable 插件的 Design-Audit-Polish 标准化设计迭代工作流</h1><p>该流程是 Impeccable 插件提供的标准化设计迭代工作流，形成可循环优化闭环。</p>\n<h2 id=\"一、整体流程闭环\"><a href=\"#一、整体流程闭环\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、整体流程闭环\"></a>一、整体流程闭环</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-plain\" data-language=\"plain\"><code class=\"language-plain\">① Design（设计） → ② Audit（审查） → ③ Critique（专业评审） → ④ Normalize（标准化） → ⑤ Polish（细节打磨）\n        ↑                                                      │\n        └──────────── 循环迭代直至视觉与交互达标 ────────────────┘</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"二、分阶段详细说明\"><a href=\"#二、分阶段详细说明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、分阶段详细说明\"></a>二、分阶段详细说明</h2><h3 id=\"1-Design-设计（初始产出）\"><a href=\"#1-Design-设计（初始产出）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. Design 设计（初始产出）\"></a>1. Design 设计（初始产出）</h3><ul>\n<li>调用方式：直接下发设计需求，或使用 <code>/impeccable</code></li>\n<li>作用：基于指定组件库&#x2F;设计规范生成初始 UI 页面代码</li>\n<li>使用示例：</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>帮我用 TDesign 组件库设计一个 AI Agent 配置页面</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>输出：完整页面结构、组件基础代码、基础布局</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-Audit-交互审查\"><a href=\"#2-Audit-交互审查\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. Audit 交互审查\"></a>2. Audit 交互审查</h3><ul>\n<li>命令：<code>/impeccable audit</code></li>\n<li>核心作用：校验用户体验、信息层级、操作流程，排查基础可用性问题</li>\n<li>检查维度：<ol>\n<li>页面信息层级是否清晰</li>\n<li>用户操作路径是否直观明确</li>\n<li>页面是否存在多余视觉噪音</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>输出样例：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-plain\" data-language=\"plain\"><code class=\"language-plain\">🔍 Audit 结果：\n- ⚠️主按钮与次要按钮对比度不足\n- ⚠️卡片间距不统一（16px&#x2F;20px 混用）\n- ✅ 整体布局符合 F 型阅读模式</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-Critique-专业设计评审\"><a href=\"#3-Critique-专业设计评审\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. Critique 专业设计评审\"></a>3. Critique 专业设计评审</h3><ul>\n<li>命令：<code>/impeccable critique</code></li>\n<li>核心作用：站在资深设计师视角做专业视觉规范评审</li>\n<li>检查维度：<ol>\n<li>配色是否匹配项目设计规范</li>\n<li>字体层级、字重对比度是否合理</li>\n<li>全页面组件视觉风格统一性</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>输出样例：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-plain\" data-language=\"plain\"><code class=\"language-plain\">🎨 Critique 结果：\n- 🔴 AI 专属紫色滥用在普通按钮（仅可用于AI功能标识）\n- 🟡 标题正文字重对比偏弱（400 vs 500，建议标题600）\n- 🟢 圆角尺寸符合规范 9px&#x2F;12px</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"4-Normalize-样式标准化\"><a href=\"#4-Normalize-样式标准化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. Normalize 样式标准化\"></a>4. Normalize 样式标准化</h3><ul>\n<li>命令：<code>/impeccable normalize</code></li>\n<li>核心作用：一键统一全局样式，消除碎片化不规范写法</li>\n<li>自动修复内容：<ol>\n<li>间距统一为 4&#x2F;8&#x2F;16&#x2F;24&#x2F;32px 标准化体系</li>\n<li>颜色值替换为项目规范预设变量</li>\n<li>圆角统一为规范尺寸 9px&#x2F;12px&#x2F;32px</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"5-Polish-细节质感打磨\"><a href=\"#5-Polish-细节质感打磨\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. Polish 细节质感打磨\"></a>5. Polish 细节质感打磨</h3><ul>\n<li>命令：<code>/impeccable polish</code></li>\n<li>核心作用：精细优化视觉细节，提升页面高级质感</li>\n<li>优化内容：<ol>\n<li>增加 hover、切换过渡微动效</li>\n<li>优化阴影分层，强化页面层次感</li>\n<li>微调图标比例、留白间隙</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"三、完整实操流程示例\"><a href=\"#三、完整实操流程示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、完整实操流程示例\"></a>三、完整实操流程示例</h2><p>场景：<code>cloudtalkAdmin</code> 项目新增知识库管理页面</p>\n<ol>\n<li>环境准备</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cd &#x2F;e&#x2F;Kuyi&#x2F;cloudtalkAdmin\nclaude</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>第一轮 - 生成基础页面（Design）</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>帮我新增一个知识库管理页面，包含搜索、列表、详情弹窗</p></blockquote>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>第二轮 - 交互可用性审查</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>&#x2F;impeccable audit</p></blockquote>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>第三轮 - 专业视觉评审</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"ro