\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>&#x2F;impeccable normalize</p></blockquote>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>第五轮 - 细节质感打磨</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>&#x2F;impeccable polish</p></blockquote>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>循环微调（按需执行）</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-plain\" data-language=\"plain\"><code class=\"language-plain\">&#x2F;impeccable bolder    # 强化页面视觉对比\n&#x2F;impeccable quieter   # 弱化视觉、降低页面厚重感\n&#x2F;impeccable animate   # 补充更多交互动效</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"四、Impeccable-高频设计命令速查表\"><a href=\"#四、Impeccable-高频设计命令速查表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、Impeccable 高频设计命令速查表\"></a>四、Impeccable 高频设计命令速查表</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>命令</th>\n<th>功能说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable audit</code></td>\n<td>页面UX、信息层级可用性审查</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable critique</code></td>\n<td>设计师视角专业视觉评审</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable normalize</code></td>\n<td>全局样式统一标准化</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable polish</code></td>\n<td>细节、阴影、留白质感精修</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable distill</code></td>\n<td>删减冗余元素，消除视觉噪音</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable bolder</code></td>\n<td>提高色彩、字号、区块视觉强度</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable quieter</code></td>\n<td>弱化高亮，降低页面视觉冲击力</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>/impeccable animate</code></td>\n<td>补充hover、切换、加载等交互动效</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>Design-Audit-Polish 是 Impeccable 插件提供的三阶段前端设计工作流：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>阶段</th>\n<th>命令</th>\n<th>作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Design</strong></td>\n<td><code>/impeccable craft</code></td>\n<td>从零创建设计</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Audit</strong></td>\n<td><code>/impeccable audit</code></td>\n<td>自动检测设计问题</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Polish</strong></td>\n<td><code>/impeccable polish</code></td>\n<td>精细化调整</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><strong>核心价值：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>把设计过程从”一次性生成”变成”迭代优化”</li>\n<li>44 条规则自动检测，减少人工审查</li>\n<li>支持 23 种子命令，覆盖字体、配色、动效、布局等维度</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>推荐用法：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>用 <code>craft</code> 快速出初稿</li>\n<li>用 <code>audit</code> 找出问题</li>\n<li>用 <code>polish</code> 系列命令逐项优化</li>\n</ol>\n<p>这个工作流特别适合对设计不敏感的开发者，用规则驱动的方式保证设计质量。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Impeccable 插件的 Design-Audit-Polish 标准化设计迭代工作流...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编程","slug":"编程","count":28,"path":"api/categories/编程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Claude Code","slug":"Claude-Code","count":8,"path":"api/tags/Claude-Code.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Impeccable-%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84-Design-Audit-Polish-%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%B5%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Impeccable 插件的 Design-Audit-Polish 标准化设计迭代工作流</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E9%97%AD%E7%8E%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、整体流程闭环</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二、分阶段详细说明</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-Design-%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%A7%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. Design 设计（初始产出）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-Audit-%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. Audit 交互审查</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-lin